The paper discusses interpretability and regularization techniques in deep neural networks, which are core topics in the field of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also presents an ensemble algorithm for arbitrary neural networks, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV). The algorithm is based on analyzing the hidden spaces of neural networks, which is a topic in neural engineering (cs.NE) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
